title: New Balance Women's 411 V1 Training Shoe
description: Whether you’re stepping out for fitness or fun, the New Balance 411v1 walking shoe is always a welcome walking companion. These casual walking shoes deliver everyday comfort and style with lightweight leather uppers featuring classic New Balance branding and breathable mesh accents. They’re a fashionable addition to your athletic wear, but can also be worn with jeans or khakis for a comfortable weekend look. A super soft lining and a plush insole keeps feet in cushioned comfort with every step, while the durable rubber outsole of these sneakers helps ensure lasting performance on a variety of surfaces. Wear these walking shoes for reliable comfort during lightweight walks and workouts or lace them up for sporty support when you’re hanging out with friends — the 411v1 has you covered wherever your day takes you.
